snippet.title: MikoVerse | Kickstarter Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mikoverse/mikoverse

Explore MikoVerse as your own avatar in rich multiplayer 3D sandbox online worlds. Build your own homes and communities on private or public servers to socialize and play!
